OL,5, Dozens more ballet dancers have        
OL,6, described body-shaming and bullying at 
OL,7, schools across the UK, following a BBC 
OL,8, investigation earlier this year.       
OL,10,FOne ex-Elmhurst Ballet School student  
OL,11,Fsays she was shut in a room by staff   
OL,12,Fwhile having a mental health crisis.   
OL,14,FAnother developed anorexia and came    
OL,15,Fclose to suicide after attending the   
OL,16,FLondon Vocational Ballet School.       
OL,18,FBoth schools said their records differ 
OL,19,Ffrom the accounts given to the BBC and 
OL,20,Fthat student welfare was a priority.   
